Key Improvements

Separated knowledge base from code, storing all content in an independent local knowledge.txt

Added local file monitoring; no need to restart the app after editing the txt

AI automatically loads the latest knowledge base on the next query, with answers updated instantly

Retained OOP structure and full exception handling from v3 for better stability

Limitations

Only supports local editing of the knowledge base; no remote modification feature

RAG retrieval not implemented, which may affect accuracy with a large knowledge base

No conversation history persistence
